    <scopecontent id="aspace_002549ce1e81ada2c7d8c59695f8ee91">
      <head>Scope and Contents</head>
      <p>The ten ledgers were organized in chronological order based on the first entry in each book. Information found in the ledgers includes: name of deceased, plot location, and date of burial.</p>
